translate portuguese counselorconversation3_535998b2:

    # pc "There's this girl that lives next door to me, Jamie."
    pc "Há uma rapariga que mora ao meu lado, a Jamie."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:10
translate portuguese counselorconversation3_dcfcdfa2:

    # pc "I can't get her out of my mind."
    pc "Não consigo tirá-la da cabeça."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:11
translate portuguese counselorconversation3_bee654f7:

    # sc "You like her?"
    sc "Gostas dela?"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:12
translate portuguese counselorconversation3_abd0877e:

    # pc "Yeah, but there's more to it than that."
    pc "Sim, mas há mais do que isso."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:13
translate portuguese counselorconversation3_c5ac6fea:

    # pc "We have a history. We dated when we were younger, but then I hurt her."
    pc "Temos um passado. Namorámos quando éramos mais novos, mas depois magoei-a."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:14
translate portuguese counselorconversation3_3b37105b:

    # pc "I didn't mean to, but I did."
    pc "Não foi de propósito, mas magoei-a."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:15
translate portuguese counselorconversation3_83b99294:

    # pc "Then I left, and now that I'm back it's sort of like we're starting over, but we still have all this history."
    pc "Depois fui-me embora e agora que voltei é como se estivéssemos a recomeçar, mas ainda temos todo esse passado."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:18
translate portuguese counselorconversation3_af5378b6:

    # pc "Do you know what I mean?"
    pc "Percebes o que quero dizer?"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:19
translate portuguese counselorconversation3_eec64a34:

    # sc "I think I do. You have memories with her, but it's almost like it's a different person because it's been so long."
    sc "Acho que sim. Tens memórias com ela, mas é quase como se fosse uma pessoa diferente, porque já passou tanto tempo."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:20
translate portuguese counselorconversation3_de5061cc:

    # pc "Exactly! I remember hanging out with her when we were younger, but both of us have changed so much it's sort of like remembering a movie."
    pc "Exatamente! Lembro-me de sair com ela quando éramos mais novos, mas ambos mudámos tanto que é como se estivéssemos a recordar um filme."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:21
translate portuguese counselorconversation3_a7dabb45:

    # sc "Does it bother you?"
    sc "Isso incomoda-te?"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:22
translate portuguese counselorconversation3_72e3f009:

    # pc "No, not at all."
    pc "Não, de todo."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:23
translate portuguese counselorconversation3_65acc085:

    # pc "It's nice actually. It's like we have a head start."
    pc "Na verdade, é bom. É como se tivéssemos uma vantagem inicial."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:24
translate portuguese counselorconversation3_46d1797b:

    # pc "What happened before isn't holding our relationship back at all. It's really like we just skipped the first couple of levels, you know? Because we already did them."
    pc "O que aconteceu antes não está a atrapalhar a nossa relação de forma alguma. É mesmo como se tivéssemos saltado os primeiros níveis, percebes? Porque já os passámos."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:25
translate portuguese counselorconversation3_abd28437:

    # sc "So things are getting serious with her?"
    sc "Então as coisas estão a ficar sérias com ela?"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:26
translate portuguese counselorconversation3_ee1883b8:

    # pc "I don't know if I'd call it serious, but we both like each other."
    pc "Não sei se diria que é sério, mas gostamos um do outro."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:27
translate portuguese counselorconversation3_d72f2f51:

    # sc "Companionship is good. You should have somebody in your life that you can rely on."
    sc "A companhia é boa. Deves ter alguém na tua vida em quem possas confiar."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:28
translate portuguese counselorconversation3_7d69eb5d:

    # sc "Somebody who makes you happy."
    sc "Alguém que te faça feliz."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:30
translate portuguese counselorconversation3_1487ed22:

    # "Her voice suddenly takes on a somber tone as she says this, as if she does not have that someone."
    "A voz dela de repente assume um tom sombrio ao dizer isto, como se ela não tivesse essa pessoa."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:31
translate portuguese counselorconversation3_5d687698:

    # "But you've seen the ring on her finger, you know that she's married."
    "Mas já viste o anel no dedo dela, sabes que ela é casada."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:35
translate portuguese counselorconversation3_3c7fbaef:

    # sc "Oh, yes I'm fine."
    sc "Ah, sim, estou bem."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:39
translate portuguese counselorconversation3_fa2bc12a:

    # sc "Good, I'm happy for you."
    sc "Ótimo, fico feliz por ti."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:41
translate portuguese counselorconversation3_fc38e4d4:

    # sc "Well it's about time for you to get to class."
    sc "Bem, está na hora de ires para a aula."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:42
translate portuguese counselorconversation3_a8c43555:

    # pc "Okay, I'll see you next time Gertrude."
    pc "Está bem, até à próxima, Gertrude."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:43
translate portuguese counselorconversation3_1b784c07:

    # sc "Bye, [pcname]."
    sc "Adeus, [pcname]."

